displayName: City of Campus, Grassland - Residential House

parameters:
Housewife Shino: Oh, aren't you the person who came before?
Have you been able to meet your friends since then?

Housewife Shino: If it's alright with you... I could take a
message in case they come to visit.

\CL The Aftermath of Phantom Thief PernoThe strange acts
caused by Phantom Thief Perno... The act of returning the
stolen items abruptly stopped one day.

\CL The guards who had been chasing after Phantom Thief
Perno for a long time were on high alert for the occurrence
of another incident, but it didn't last long.

\CL Eventually, the existence of Phantom Thief Perno was
forgotten as time passed.

\CL The Aftermath of Housewife ShinoShe spends her days in
harmony with her beloved husband. She becomes famous in the
neighborhood as a kind and beautiful woman.

\CL She was blessed with children and gave birth to three
beautiful girls.

\CL She cherished a diary that had become tattered
throughout her life, and she never showed its contents to
even her beloved husband.

You won't be able to come back, but are you really leaving
the room?
Clea (We haven't talked yet, have we?)
I'm going to meet the explorer Armada if(!s[411])
I'm going to meet the Voice Priestess Phoni if(!s[412])
I'm going to meet the one-armed Opro if(!s[413])
I'm going to meet the Phantom Thief Perno if(!s[414])
I'm going to meet Cors, the wanderer if(!s[415])
I'm going to meet Goat from the Bulk Gang if(!s[416])
I'm going to meet with the former Imperial Dark Division, Luid if(!s[417])

Clea: Please convey to my friends that it was an honor to
witness this new milestone.

Shino the Housewife: I was able to witness a wonderful scene
of taking a new step forward.

Housewife Shino: It's a coincidence, but I was also able to
take a new step forward... I was able to achieve the
ordinary life that has been my dream for many years.

Mage Relm: The most surprising thing was their physical
abilities, being able to control even the magic that I
didn't know about...

Housewife Shino: I think magic is just a tool, and if the
user is not skilled, even a greatsword becomes a mere stick.

Mage Relm: As you said, it may be true. I also want to train
my body to become an Archmage!

Thief Nora: Um, well, I shouldn't say this! But I was really
happy to receive praise about being a thief from that
person.

Housewife Shino: Being a thief is not something to be
praised... but if your skills are being praised, it's okay
to be genuinely happy.

Thief Nora: Yes, thank you very much! I will absolutely,
absolutely keep my promise with that person!

Priestess Sophia: They seem so happy, it's quite enviable. I
plan to return to the campus, so if you have the time,
please come by.

Housewife Shino: That's wonderful! Since you seem to like
wine, I'll prepare something of high quality for you.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, that's good. Let's make sure neither
of us becomes loose-lipped, okay?
